<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="signal-v">signal <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'sɪɡnəl/    美 /'sɪɡnəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>vi &amp; vt 发信号；示意：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>signalled</strong> widly <strong>for</strong> help, but nobody noticed.
他拼命地发信号求助，但是没人注意到。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The bell <strong>signalled that</strong> school was over.
铃声响起，放学了。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>In order not to be heard, she pointed her finger upwards to <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (示意) that someone was moving about upstairs.   （2015 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. signal  </p></div>